snippet.title: The Sims 4 Spooky Stuff: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Carve pumpkins and scare up some fun with The Sims 4 Spooky Stuff!
 
Learn more about this Stuff Pack: http://o.ea.com/43140
 
Decorate your Sim’s home with ghoulishly fun décor and invite friends over for a spooky party! Dress up in all-new costumes, carve pumpkins, and offer your guests a treat from the spooky candy bowl.

#sims4
